<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Yunike Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border: 1px dashed #ccc;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      padding-top: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Verification Code</h1>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your verification code for {{action}} on Yunike is:</p>
    
    <div class="code">{{otpCode}}</div>
    
    <p>This code will expire in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this code, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from Yunike. Do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Yunike. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 